Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:06.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,At that day...\NKyuto's reset button
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:11.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,was pressed. Since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:19.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't exactly know a place where I can think properly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:24.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Something inside me has stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:28.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:31.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything seems so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:34.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand the words they say,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.21,0:00:36.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even see people around me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.77,0:00:39.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:42.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:45.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:51.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear nothing.. I see nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:56.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a human, still alive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:01:00.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, Kyuto is not around anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.69,0:01:03.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:06.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.70,0:01:10.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:16.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ok even if its not the real thing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:20.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ok just to see her once
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:23.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even from a distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:25.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:49.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:53.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Found it! Look
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:57.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? Have you found what you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:59.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:03.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you charge her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:08.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what you've said to Fukai-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:11.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai can only do nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:12.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:15.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You definitely can't do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:21.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was thinking that you only want Fukai-kun to press the reset button
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:25.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, thinking of its possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:30.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I changed Kyuto's reset button
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:33.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time comes that Fukai-kun will press the button
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:37.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Kyuto to pretend to reset
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:42.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I want to see it with my own eyes and run here as soon as I can but,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:46.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,With my appearance, it seems like they ran away properly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:53.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Kyuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:56.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you attached something like transmitters?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:58.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:02:59.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:07.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't bring back Q10, something terrible is bound to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:10.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Something terrible"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:13.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The world will be distorted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:20.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, explain it to Fukai-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:22.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you'll convince him to agree with you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:24.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:31.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,People will only believe in what they see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:37.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I explain it to him, he won't believe me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:42.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you let Fukai-kun see something in order to threaten him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:49.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course there is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,To appeal heartily
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:57.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:03.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still in year 2010 you know
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:05.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,that is a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:36.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. It's Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:41.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please Santa,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:46.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see Kyuto once again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:50.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If such miracle happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:54.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa~ wa~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:56.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,wa~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:05:02.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow! Snow! Snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:05.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto?\NNot in a loud voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:11.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am seen~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run away~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:51.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If such miracle happens
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:57.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to ask anything in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:32.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's with the tea?\NThen I didn't press the reset button?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:34.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:37.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why is Kyuto staying in your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:41.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Professor Yanagi relies on me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:44.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh~\NBut why you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:50.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you feel but just to remind you\NThis is my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:52.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:55.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why dressing like Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:58.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We were told not to go out,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:01.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kyuto kept on telling me to try win the lottery
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:06.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, in order to go, she has to disguise as Santa
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:08.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:11.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have luck in lottery?\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:14.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto won! She won 3 times!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Look~~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, this is my room!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:32.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:59.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh..voice is coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:03.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You feel bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be 1 week today
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:17.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been 1 week? why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:21.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it by accident when I came
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:26.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't want you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:29.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're happy right now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:34.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not your place anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:36.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:42.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it myself because of my scared face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:48.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I come here everyday not entering the ward
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:53.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If I am found out, Kubo-kun will feel bad. What will I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:58.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the courage at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:06.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,My love for him is not enough right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:23.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm putting back the original reset button
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:26.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Why? If you do that, Fujino Tsukiko will again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:32.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, if reset button is to be pressed, Fukai-kun will do it himself
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:39.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai will definitely not press it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:42.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you agree to communicate with Fujino-san, maybe you'll understand what's in her heart
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:45.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Her heart? Talk to her? There's no way I'm going to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If the button is pressed, the same thing happens again
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You wont understand what will really happen when you press this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:58.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If given the chance to press it, the outcome is completely different
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:02.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it Fukai will be the one to press it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:08.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:11.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:13.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:22.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Kyuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:26.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, Fukai-kun is easy to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:32.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you press the reset button?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:34.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No way
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:40.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you leave Kyuto the way it is, the world will change significantly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:48.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of your actions, two civilizations will go into extinction and one language will be destroyed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:50.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't get my point?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:56.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, somewhere in this world, there are 900 million people starving
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:11:02.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm saying right now is, people are dying because of war and conflicts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:07.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But for you, it has nothing to do with you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:11.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, someone has lost an important person somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:14.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Until that person is not able to shed out tear anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:18.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Since,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:22.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't have the same perspective, you won't be able to see it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not going to press it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:32.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,People die?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:39.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,5.6 million people
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:49.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious. Fujino Tsukiko is lying
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:51.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be better
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:58.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that one over there. Is that the desk of Fujioka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:12:02.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you mention it, Fujioka's seat is lost
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:09.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Fujioka is doing well?\NSomehow, I haven't seen him everyday
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:11.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like there is great distance between us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:14.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a bakeshop just around the corner
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:16.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:19.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! By the way, I haven't seen Kyuto for such a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:25.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll tell her to come to school tomorrow right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:28.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok!\NEh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:31.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? So it is.\NSomething happened? Is she sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how come Nakao-kun knows her whereabouts?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:36.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It's not like we're dating or something
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:38.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We're definitely not dating!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:41.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody is thinking that way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still there
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:48.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as everybody can have a long rest. They couldn't care less
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'll be in Canada, what will I do there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:54.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like what everyone feels inside, we will all die eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto is absent for almost a week
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:07.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know something?\NNo..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:13.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm sorry for asking. I thought you and Yamamoto are good friends
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:15.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like I'm mistaken. Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:29.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:32.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really the worst
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:33.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:37.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Yamamoto-san is my friend but,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:39.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't noticed her absence at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:42.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:45.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaa...But right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:48.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,you're even listening to my complaints
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:52.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really the worst
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:54.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sort of..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:59.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:10.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to say "I'm waiting for you upon your return from Canada"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:13.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter what, I can't say it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:18.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe because I don't have expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:23.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you don't have expectations
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:29.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I also think so
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:32.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be ok in Canada? I'm still lost
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:39.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:43.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,start believing in ourselves first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:48.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it, nothing will eventually start
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:56.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Only for now
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I a bit arrogant?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:11.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's just for now right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:18.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels good. Let's decorate together next year
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:23.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's live together next year, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can't do that\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:29.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never know what lies ahead if we don't try
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:34.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't expect much from different things
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:40.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I've managed to eat well.\NBut there are worst situations that I avoid
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:43.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm just plain stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:45.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:50.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Right now I just bore you. Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:55.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No.. I think that's a brilliant idea
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:57.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:16:02.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that brings harmony in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:09.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,People in this world somehow manages to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:14.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,and still can avoid any worst situations
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:53.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?\NOh
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:57.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wake him up.\NNo.. let him sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:05.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he draw this carelessly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:08.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, there are 4 people. He draws faces of anyone he randomly met
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:17.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I look at this picture, he is not lost
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:20.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"I have faith that he will come back"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:24.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When I look at this picture, he's probably realized
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:27.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,that you're coming
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:33.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What I mean is, his wish is granted
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:36.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas present
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:39.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't open it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:44.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?\NBecause it's empty
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:49.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be with him next year\NI'll be your substitute
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:50.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going now?\NOh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:53.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:18:00.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all I got
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:03.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's ok
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:06.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, It's been decided
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:07.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:10.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it all
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:13.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll get this
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:19.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:32.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe its true..\N5.6 million people will die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:36.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For me, what Fujino-san said is probably true
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:38.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,5.6 million people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:41.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,With regard to that number, I don't know what it means
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:44.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are certain things that naturally disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:47.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's balance
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:51.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the worst thing that's gonna happen?\NHmm~ that is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:54.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with you if anything happens
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:57.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Don't you think that's weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:19:02.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of my actions, as a consequence, something terrible will happen
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:06.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is not fair you know
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:10.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, it's getting complicated
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:13.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Worst things are going to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:19.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This came out from Kyuto's tooth
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:23.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:27.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter from you at 88 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:31.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:33.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:41.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how will I read this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:54.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to say this to my 18-year old self"\NRight there
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:59.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"I loved Q10 as much as I loved the world"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:19.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to meet the music producer\NI'm so excited
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:22.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that when you wish something from this doll, it'll come true
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:24.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:28.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we have our CD debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:31.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not working
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:34.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it\NHuh? Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:36.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,please~~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:43.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's impossible for us to have CD debut, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:48.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wish for something else then
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:56.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...\NIt's granted! What did you wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:01.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:04.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The producers will come!\NTamiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:25.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish is granted
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:29.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish is..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:34.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be able to graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:42.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, we're leaving this hospital together,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:47.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to walk that road going towards the school gate
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:55.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not possible next year, then we'll do it a year after next
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:21:59.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If not possible a year after next, then we'll do it on the third year
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:04.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I said deep in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:08.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this thing released light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:13.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my wishes will not be granted...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.95,0:22:22.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the school gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:26.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,that we can walk through together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.39,0:22:32.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When that time comes, I
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.89,0:22:36.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,will not wear wig
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.40,0:22:38.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,My hair will remain red,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:42.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will flaunt it so that everyone can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:44.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk with you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:10.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have hard toast?\NOh sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:14.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This store has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.38,0:23:17.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We have hard toast but it'll be out soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.92,0:23:19.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you wait for a while?\NSure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:23.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then\NExcuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:27.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So how is it? You can still go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:29.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:31.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to do well with the society,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:34.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,First of, it would be nice to become a dependable adult where a single person can rely on you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:36.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,and half of that person's success
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.41,0:23:38.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,is influenced by the dependable adult
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.93,0:23:41.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How's my idea? Do you have that person who is a good influence to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.48,0:23:42.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:46.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you! Who is that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:49.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you. Principal
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:53.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me? So it's me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.89,0:23:56.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No way~ really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.39,0:23:59.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also going to do my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:02.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard toast is now available
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.88,0:24:08.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, that baked bread is crunchy
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.39,0:24:13.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Really? Oh I see
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.38,0:24:17.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah~ This smells good
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.45,0:24:23.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm holding a warm bread
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.39,0:24:26.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a daughter and grandchild at home
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.89,0:24:30.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And I have a student who believes in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.88,0:24:34.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm happy
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.38,0:24:53.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.38,0:24:55.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.37,0:25:00.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you love mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.37,0:25:01.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.91,0:25:08.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to say it?\NYou want me to say it here? In the living room?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.90,0:25:14.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. I love her
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.90,0:25:17.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Most especially her neck
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.89,0:25:21.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.38,0:25:25.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,the way you love mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.40,0:25:27.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,is the same as you love the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.95,0:25:30.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you mention it, I probably also have
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.89,0:25:32.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,As I am loving your mother more,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.91,0:25:36.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have loved the world already
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.38,0:25:42.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Really? What do you mean of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.88,0:25:47.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I love your mother..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.45,0:25:50.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,and I love the children that were born from your mother
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.91,0:25:53.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, your mother gave birth to you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.39,0:25:56.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,your mother and I love you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.90,0:26:00.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I also love the kindness that your mother has given to us
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.88,0:26:04.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind person is someone who loves kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.90,0:26:08.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother can be ill-tempered, sometimes even bossy..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.99,0:26:11.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the recent personality of your mother..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.90,0:26:15.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am also loving that personality too
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.88,0:26:21.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother stands up composed. I just love everything about her
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.39,0:26:24.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I can say
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.91,0:26:28.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Q-chan~~
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.98,0:26:31.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back~
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.88,0:26:34.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I love kind-hearted Kyuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.88,0:26:37.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning\NOh! Long time no see
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.89,0:26:43.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I love the way Kyuto's stand which is composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.89,0:26:50.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The way I love Kyuto..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.48,0:26:52.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,is the same as the way I love the world
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.89,0:26:57.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,First of,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.39,0:27:00.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,will you press the reset button here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.38,0:27:05.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.90,0:27:10.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita's heart is anxious
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.89,0:27:18.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If your heart continues to be like that, will you be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.90,0:27:28.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be able to attain happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.00,0:28:13.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll press the reset button.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.06,0:28:18.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.52,0:28:26.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.02,0:28:30.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to say the good news
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.51,0:28:38.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto said that the human brain's memory will always be there since it is made as such
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.01,0:28:39.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.55,0:28:44.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,After 1 year, Kyuto won't be able to remember anything
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.52,0:28:47.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am also like her
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.51,0:28:55.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,All our memories will gradually fade away. You don't need to worry about it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.01,0:28:59.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I must forget Kyuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.03,0:29:03.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Christmas miracle,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.01,0:29:07.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\NThere's no way that I'll forget her
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.51,0:29:10.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.52,0:29:17.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai is going to press it after all
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.07,0:29:25.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, for the last time, can you give me strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.03,0:29:27.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, which
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.00,0:29:30.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto can also do just like a robot\NTo gather the power by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.00,0:29:33.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Grant you power?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.51,0:29:41.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Puff!! Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.61,0:29:46.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Puff! Puff! Puff!\NPuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.03,0:29:48.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Puff!!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.52,0:29:51.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Granted!!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.45,0:30:03.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say my farewell also to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.54,0:30:05.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.44,0:30:07.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.94,0:30:09.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.45,0:30:12.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.95,0:30:15.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.\NSee you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.45,0:30:18.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.\NBye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.44,0:30:19.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.94,0:30:22.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!\NSee you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.49,0:30:24.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.03,0:30:26.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow\NSee you tomorrow. Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.96,0:30:29.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.97,0:30:31.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow~!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.47,0:30:35.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.97,0:30:37.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Till tomorrow then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.46,0:30:43.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.\NOh! See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.03,0:30:47.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.94,0:30:57.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody says "there's tomorrow"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.96,0:31:01.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They believe in it no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.95,0:31:05.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something that can't be taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.49,0:31:11.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody will take it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.54,0:31:15.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.45,0:31:21.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to forget Kyuto
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.45,0:31:25.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If the love of two person is truthful then,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.44,0:31:28.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet again someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.47,0:31:35.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth\NThere's no goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.45,0:31:43.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...Hey that's too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.96,0:31:45.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's much better if it's hand drawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.96,0:31:47.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand drawn?\NYeah
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.45,0:32:00.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, when I say hand drawn, it doesn't mean you have to draw a hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.46,0:32:03.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevermind.. just continue what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.95,0:32:10.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Rabbit!\NWow! It's a rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.95,0:32:15.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Puff.\NThis is good. Yup. This is good
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.49,0:32:19.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't find a rabbit with 5 ears in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.06,0:32:21.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Rabbit\NYup.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.43,0:32:29.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.46,0:32:37.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.44,0:32:41.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.97,0:32:50.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.58,0:33:55.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The people of this era,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.06,0:33:59.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,believes in something that they can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.08,0:34:04.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You said, "there's no eternity" right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.07,0:34:07.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.08,0:34:09.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So what you see in year 2010,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.60,0:34:13.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,are all eternal scenes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.59,0:34:19.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see..
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.14,0:34:25.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I can have my own "eternity"?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.58,0:34:30.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See! Even you think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.08,0:34:34.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe in forces that can't be seen
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.07,0:34:41.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The brain's memory is made as such?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.63,0:34:45.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we have to forget Kyuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.58,0:34:50.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Her memory will be gone after 1 year
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.09,0:34:54.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't do that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.07,0:34:59.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if everyone can do that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.59,0:35:16.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Somebody is coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.58,0:35:19.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have decided to accept boarders.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.10,0:35:20.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.60,0:35:23.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you consulting me such important things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.09,0:35:25.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But... a luggage is already inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.09,0:35:29.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! I don't like it! Wait..I have to refuse! I have to refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.17,0:35:30.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.59,0:35:35.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of me from now on.\NI'm Yanagi Ritsuko~
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.60,0:35:41.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! What is this?\NYou mean Professor Yanagi is our boarder?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.59,0:35:44.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.11,0:35:46.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have told you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.16,0:35:49.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lets live together next year"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.09,0:35:53.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi old hag! Hurry up, prepare the food already!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.08,0:35:56.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's "old hag"?\NHurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.09,0:35:59.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down! Sit down!\NAh... then...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.59,0:36:02.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You too sensei.\NSorry..
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.61,0:36:06.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,After the surgery, 6 years have passed by so quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.16,0:36:08.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't fast.\NFeeling of "finally" right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.56,0:36:13.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's 6 years you know.\NRight... so I should say "already" right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.07,0:36:17.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Working hard with everyone, just like a normal family does,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.09,0:36:19.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It was good experience
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.58,0:36:23.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, from here on, Heita will say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.11,0:36:27.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Me? What will I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.58,0:36:29.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh....
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.57,0:36:35.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,With regard to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.57,0:36:40.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Definitely will be cured" and "believing that it will happen"...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.58,0:36:44.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will always carry it in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.65,0:36:47.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.58,0:36:58.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When you come back, what's the first thing you're going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.58,0:37:02.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.12,0:37:04.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,To climb the school gate's hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.07,0:37:08.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.09,0:37:13.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And then to skip class and lie down at the rooftop
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.06,0:37:17.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,humming next to someone who's singing,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.57,0:37:20.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,While staring at the blue sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.60,0:37:25.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,whatever feelings is about to start from then on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.10,0:37:35.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not "about to start"...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.07,0:37:41.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It has already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.60,0:38:06.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't go back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.08,0:38:08.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.57,0:38:11.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For the last time, let me see you smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.60,0:38:15.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be impossible for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.17,0:38:19.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be alright.\NYou can go on living with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.09,0:38:39.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, this is definitely the one
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.65,0:38:42.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.58,0:38:46.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I had wild ideas during my high school days.\NEven if it's just your imagination,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.07,0:38:49.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,you have this in your heart wherever you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.07,0:38:52.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure someone out there is just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.16,0:38:56.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... Maybe..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.57,0:39:02.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto was always watching you just like watching a scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.57,0:39:06.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Lecture is about to start. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.09,0:39:07.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh.. right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.07,0:39:17.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. You will smile
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.09,0:39:22.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl... she will be my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.07,0:39:25.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You were together until you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.60,0:39:30.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So now, you can forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.65,0:39:37.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,that Kyuto was here.\NYou just continue believing in people
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.07,0:40:31.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.\NWas I too loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.08,0:40:38.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Just nostalgic
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.07,0:40:42.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This sound is nice right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.57,0:41:00.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was 88 years old yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.09,0:41:03.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to die yet
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.09,0:41:06.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, for my wife, she thinks that perhaps I'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.60,0:41:12.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,My wife kept on asking me about Kyuto
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.57,0:41:19.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto is probably a creation of my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.07,0:41:21.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But..
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.58,0:41:27.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I look into something, Kyuto will probably show up
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.08,0:41:31.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have first seen her in a business trip from moon to earth
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.69,0:41:35.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that we had our honeymoon to a place where glacier melted
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.57,0:41:41.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The children took 1000 years to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.08,0:41:47.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of miracle will you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.58,0:42:00.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,My wife doesn't have much time to live.\NSo she wished to see me as 18 year old
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.58,0:42:04.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,To grant her wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.09,0:42:08.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,a robot that can time-travel was ordered
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.57,0:42:13.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They copied the face and all data of my wife
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.18,0:42:20.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised when they showed me the completed robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.07,0:42:23.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought it would look like Kyuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.59,0:42:27.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, they even made the same model.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.09,0:42:30.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of my springtime,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.58,0:42:36.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It was certain, this Kyuto was here.\NI was convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.64,0:42:40.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon enough, I bid farewell to my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.09,0:42:44.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there's a limit to my existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.08,0:42:49.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will see the smiling face of my wife.\NIt won't fade away.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.60,0:42:53.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that I would be following,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.07,0:42:58.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto for 70 years.\NShe was really there
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.67,0:43:06.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm beside my wife drinking tea.\NAnd I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.58,0:43:11.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm certain that love, courage and peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.07,0:43:16.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,do exist in this world" and,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.58,0:43:20.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to say this to my 18-year old self,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.67,0:43:28.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved Kyuto as much as I loved the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.09,0:43:34.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it even though I can't see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.08,0:43:39.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, you'll believe it when you see it with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.58,0:43:47.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It will appear in some way.\NUntil then.
